04c8e5fda5f302b57","tid":1578422,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrCkLxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrCkLxO.jpg&h=0e7cfdb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條仆街事後仲要比like支持馬會決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />厚面皮到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWwtUq9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWwtUq9.png&h=bf5d9602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有年長馬迷屌鳩佢仲即刻報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQpvojv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQpvojv.jpg&h=bf43963d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有馬迷係立法會叫何君堯隻馬唔好再參賽 被何君堯屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PBLZgEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPBLZgEv.jpg&h=cd1de522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條撚樣返到屋企仲叫馬迷小心d 話再見到就殺無赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856e602a324589dc799327db397b7ebb2e0e4c26","tid":1578422,"uid":237733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71de7574a4683ce83cf92de864c03fb7bc88c7e3","tid":1578422,"uid":221777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4457ce7867624af84f784b139565180305b0141c","tid":1578422,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T12:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nqctagq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnqctagq.png&h=7fed4eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友係福建人<br />\n<br />\n佢話何生琴日係街比馬迷鬧係過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n新聞訪問阿叔又係咁鬧何生<br />\n<br />\n何生依家準備吹大雞要打馬迷 開始召集福建幫<br />\n<br />\n仲話呢排一見到有人拎馬經就話要打<br />\n<br />\n佢地今次唔係針對果班暴徒曱甴<br />\n<br />\n係針對我地班馬迷 各位黎緊跑馬既馬迷要小心！<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安"},{"pid":"df09119c8fe4b3f0acfb5f2419ed101e496d6e63","tid":1578422,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"}]}